        "author": "jgm",
        "category": "Consensus R\u0026D",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "Not that I know of.  You're best off querying a local beacon node as validator info is quite large, but if not you could use (e.g.):\n\n```\ncurl -s http://mainnet-consensus.attestant.io/eth/v1/beacon/states/head/validators | jq -r .data[].validator.withdrawal_credentials | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -10\n\n 269070 0x010000000000000000000000b9d7934878b5fb9610b3fe8a5e441e8fad7e293f\n  45347 0x010000000000000000000000210b3cb99fa1de0a64085fa80e18c22fe4722a1b\n  45316 0x0100000000000000000000008e609ac80f4324e499a6efd24f221a2caa868224\n  13045 0x0100000000000000000000001cedc0f3af8f9841b0a1f5c1a4ddc6e1a1629074\n  12349 0x010000000000000000000000e839a3e9efb32c6a56ab7128e51056585275506c\n  11208 0x010000000000000000000000eee27662c2b8eba3cd936a23f039f3189633e4c8\n   8451 0x0100000000000000000000007e2a2fa2a064f693f0a55c5639476d913ff12d05\n   6366 0x0100000000000000000000008306300ffd616049fd7e4b0354a64da835c1a81c\n   5300 0x010000000000000000000000a8c62111e4652b07110a0fc81816303c42632f64\n   4452 0x0100000000000000000000006357e4bdaff733dfe8f50d12d07c03b3bed0884b\n```",
        "created_at": "2023-09-04T14:27:27.963000+00:00",
